description: GemBox.Spreadsheet is a .NET component that enables developers to read, write, convert and print spreadsheet files (XLSX, XLS, ODS, CSV, HTML, PDF or XPS) from their .NET applications using one simple API.
releaseNotes:
- Fixed XLSX reading issue when using ExcelFile.LoadFromDirectory() method.
- Fixed XLSX reading issue with reading files that exceed ExcelFile.GroupMethodsAffectedCellsLimit.
- Fixed XLSX writing issue with writing SlantDashDot line style.
- Fixed issue with measuring text size.
- Fixed XLSX reading issue with reading cell value.
- Several internal zip components are replaced with DotNetZip library.
- Added HTML writing support for writing data-cell attribute with cell address.
- Fixed XLSX writing issue with writing very large number of similar columns.
- Fixed issue with auto-fitting rows which contain merged cells.
- Fixed issue with inserting pictures.
- Fixed issue with deleting pictures.
summary: GemBox.Spreadsheet is a .NET component for reading and writing spreadsheet files (XLSX, XLS, CSV, ODS, HTML, PDF and XPS).
